# ║ Path(imul_num(p, ), multiply inplace the polynomial p by an element in the coefficient ring, provided p is not one of the generators; else multiply not inplace) over Any ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ imul_num : Any → Any                                       ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ Trusted:                                                   ║
# ║   z3.Solver.check                                          ║
